Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.65,0:00:04.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Optimus, you are not going to believe this.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.28,0:00:08.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just pinpointed the location of the Decepticon warship.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.77,0:00:12.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How did you penetrate their cloaking technology?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.72,0:00:13.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.98,0:00:18.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was experimenting the variable frequency wavelengths when I stumbled upon it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.74,0:00:25.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even still, their ship must be experiencing some kind of electromagnetic breach.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.41,0:00:28.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With Megatron deceased and the element of surprise...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.83,0:00:31.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can cause some serious damage.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.15,0:00:38.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Also in the same frequency, an Autobot emergency beacon.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.18,0:00:43.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Decepticons can wait, there maybe Autobots in distress.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.58,0:00:45.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rachet, bring your medical kit.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.37,0:01:00.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A crash landing, buried here for centuries.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.78,0:01:13.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If they traveled in stasis mode, there may be survivors.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.39,0:01:40.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Optimus, these Autobots didn't perish in the crash.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.94,0:01:44.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They are displaying the effects of a virus.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.91,0:01:46.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a plague ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.35,0:01:49.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't touch anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.89,0:01:52.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The virus could still be active.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.35,0:02:05.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.90,0:03:01.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cybonic plague.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.88,0:03:06.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's only contagious if contact is made with the infected energeon.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.98,0:03:09.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(192,280)}What was a plague doing in an Autobot spaceship?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.91,0:03:11.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(192,280)}Its passengers were infected.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.88,0:03:14.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(192,280)}The virus wiped out millions on Cybertron during the great war.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.28,0:03:19.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(192,280)}Cybonic plague was engineered in the Decepticons' Biological Warfare Program...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.16,0:03:22.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(192,280)}by Megatron himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.58,0:03:25.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have a cure, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.06,0:03:30.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No cure...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.59,0:03:34.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Optimus, please, save your strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.70,0:03:37.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would Megatron create a disease without having a cure?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.35,0:03:39.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean what if he caught it by accident?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.36,0:03:41.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like we can ask Megatron, Jack.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.80,0:03:43.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's pushing up lugnuts.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.88,0:03:48.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(192,280)}But we might be able to access the Decepticon database.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.08,0:03:52.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For the moment, we still have a fix on their warship's location.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.54,0:03:54.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bumblebee, come with.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.03,0:03:58.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(192,280)}Arcee, quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.41,0:04:11.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's start with the lab.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.26,0:04:34.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm in the network.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.91,0:04:39.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rachet...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.06,0:04:43.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Were you...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.61,0:04:46.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Infected? No.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.02,0:04:51.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it's here, I don't see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.91,0:04:53.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you certain, Arcee?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.89,0:04:56.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I searched every file, nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.28,0:04:59.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, search again! Clearly you missed something!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.94,0:05:02.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I scanned the entire database.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.32,0:05:06.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you use a redundant quantum algorithm?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.16,0:05:07.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me how to research.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.89,0:05:09.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think you are the only one who cares about Optimus?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.81,0:05:13.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.13,0:05:15.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it? What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.66,0:05:23.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Megatron.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.07,0:05:26.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.51,0:05:28.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.76,0:05:30.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.12,0:05:32.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm staring right at him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.11,0:05:35.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good news is,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.48,0:05:37.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Megatron isn't exactly staring back.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.11,0:05:39.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Megatron?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.10,0:05:43.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's critical, hooked up to life support.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.45,0:05:47.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Time to finish this once and for all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.89,0:05:49.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! Don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.68,0:05:51.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One good reason, fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.72,0:05:54.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Megatron may be Optimus's only hope for survival.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.25,0:05:56.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.41,0:05:58.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does he display brainwave activity?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.42,0:06:03.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Spiking hard, his sick mind still at work.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.24,0:06:09.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perfect. If a cure exists, Megatron maybe the only one who knows it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.48,0:06:13.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must enter his brain and find it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.80,0:06:24.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Enter Megatron's brain?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.18,0:06:26.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rachet, are you out of your fragging mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.42,0:06:31.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Decepticon laboratory should contain all the equipment you need for a cortical psychic patch.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.80,0:06:35.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way. Have you ever even performed the procedure?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.71,0:06:40.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. But I have thoroughly studied the theoretical literature...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.32,0:06:45.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,invented by Decepticons, outlawed by Autobots.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.45,0:06:50.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, can't we just haul Megatron through the GroundBridge, buy us some time to figure this out?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.20,0:06:53.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Time is one thing that Optimus does not have!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.70,0:06:55.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One of you must try this！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.70,0:07:01.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will not allow Optimus to pass knowing that Megatron will outlive him!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.31,0:07:06.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ratchet, I would lay down my life for Optimus, anytime, anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.07,0:07:09.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But a mind-body split...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.15,0:07:12.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You will?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.22,0:07:15.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you... sure, Bumblebee?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.94,0:07:18.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bee's the best scout there is.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.82,0:07:30.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why has the elctromagnetic shielding not been repaired?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.97,0:07:33.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The crews are working as quickly as they can, Lord...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.00,0:07:36.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are leaking a trail!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.02,0:07:43.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All the Autobots need do to pinpoint our position is to access the correct frequency wavelength.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.34,0:07:44.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Accelerate your efforts!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.42,0:07:47.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Lord Starscream.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.50,0:07:52.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doctor in the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.71,0:07:58.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, Knock Out, and how is the patient doing today?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.52,0:07:59.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Same old...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.79,0:08:06.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An inglorious fate that he should remain in this vegetative state...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.48,0:08:10.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the contrary, Megatron's body may be scrap metal,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.61,0:08:13.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but his mind is still percolating.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.77,0:08:15.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep that to yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.31,0:08:19.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That blasted Soundwave sees and hears everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.40,0:08:21.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The eyes and ears of the Decepticons.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.29,0:08:27.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, as long as their master remains in limbo, so does their cause.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.26,0:08:31.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Decepticons deserve a strong, alert leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.89,0:08:35.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One who would require a loyal second-in-command.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.15,0:08:45.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmhmhm, a candidate would need to earn that post by making a strong case to said eyes and ears.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.49,0:08:49.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A case for showing mercy, Lord Starscream?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.97,0:08:54.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You scratch my back, I scratch yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.07,0:09:17.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ratchet, we are ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.90,0:09:20.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Initiate cortical psychic patch.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.75,0:09:44.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Communications downlink activated.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.27,0:09:46.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This will allow us to see and hear everything Bumblebee does
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.91,0:09:49.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,while within Megatron's subconscious mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.48,0:09:52.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, where is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.40,0:09:58.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bee says it looks like Kaon, the Decepticon Capital back on Cybertron.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.62,0:10:03.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ratch, Optimus's vitals.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.39,0:10:05.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.66,0:10:08.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quickly, Bumblebee.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.22,0:10:09.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know you are in unknown territory,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.81,0:10:13.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but you must figure out where information might be filed in Megatron's mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.38,0:10:25.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bumblebee, that is not Optimus,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.51,0:10:27.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but a figment of Megatron's mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.31,0:10:29.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It cannot see or hear you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.58,0:10:33.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mmmmhahaha, Optimus Prime!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.15,0:10:35.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your Autobot armies are defeated.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.73,0:10:38.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bow before your new master.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.77,0:10:40.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Never, Megatron.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.05,0:10:44.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One shall stand, one shall fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.95,0:10:46.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So be it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.50,0:11:05.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That never happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.05,0:11:07.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not a memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.49,0:11:13.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're seeing Kaon as Megatron has recreated it in his darkest dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.29,0:11:23.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Megatron, your treachery ends here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.58,0:11:38.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Autobot scout.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.39,0:11:44.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The punishment for trespassing in my domain is your destruction!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.52,0:11:59.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can this be?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.19,0:12:08.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Megatron can't touch Bee?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.85,0:12:12.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because he's not a creation of Megatron's mind,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.14,0:12:15.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bumblebee is immune to his physical attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.17,0:12:19.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are not wearing phase displacement armor.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.38,0:12:24.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your eyes track my movements, so you are not a hologram.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.95,0:12:28.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I do not believe in spirits.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.41,0:12:32.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So tell me, scout, what are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.41,0:12:33.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Megatron!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.79,0:12:43.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uho, special guest stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.24,0:12:45.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is not good.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.84,0:13:10.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are real. They were not!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.49,0:13:17.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hehehe, a cortical psychic patch.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.58,0:13:19.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How unexpected.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.75,0:13:22.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've stirred Megatron from his oblivion.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.63,0:13:24.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's becoming self-aware.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.91,0:13:28.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If this is my subconscious,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.10,0:13:31.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,what are you doing inside my head?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.60,0:13:39.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, Bee. What are you doing in there?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.06,0:13:50.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Knock Out, if you would be so kind as to provide your expert medical opinion to Soundwave,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.49,0:13:53.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,for the historical record.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.03,0:13:59.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Simply put, unaided, Megatron could remain in this deadless slumber forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.51,0:14:04.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our master would not have wanted to be seen this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.30,0:14:11.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To stand idly by while he remains captive in his own body, is not just.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.78,0:14:22.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brainwave activity, not evidence of consciousness, but merely of an endless dream
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.99,0:14:25.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,from which Megatron may never wake.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.83,0:14:31.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Soundwave, we must face reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.58,0:14:34.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Megatron is lost to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.57,0:14:38.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The only honorable option, would be to show him mercy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.93,0:14:41.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A simple throw off the switch.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.60,0:14:44.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quick, painless, compassionate.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.02,0:14:46.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ratchet, are you hearing this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.89,0:14:48.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If Megatron perishes,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.97,0:14:53.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bumblebee's mind will remain separated from his body, forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.98,0:14:55.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll lose Bumblebee and Optimus?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.47,0:15:04.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The only way you could have entered my mind, is via cortical psychic patch.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.69,0:15:06.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the question remains...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.71,0:15:09.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.13,0:15:33.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The SpaceBridge explosion.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.71,0:15:40.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And yet if, if you're in my head, I am not one with the Allspark.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.97,0:15:44.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So tell me, scout, do I still function?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.74,0:15:47.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bumblebee, we are out of time!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.39,0:15:56.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cybonic plague?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.41,0:16:00.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Somebody beside myself is, is unwell?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.14,0:16:05.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Optimus!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.46,0:16:12.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Such irony!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.41,0:16:15.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That after ages of endless battle,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.03,0:16:21.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the mighty Optimus Prime is fell by a simple virus from the distant past!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.84,0:16:27.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And what makes you think I would save the life of my oldest enemy?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.94,0:16:30.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Megatron, your treachery is...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.80,0:16:40.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, and just what is it that I want most, scout?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.56,0:16:49.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Haha, did you not see, I do slay Optimus by my own hand,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.87,0:16:52.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,at will, whenever I desire!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.09,0:17:01.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bee told Megatron if he lets the plague virus destroy the real Optimus,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.78,0:17:04.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Megatron will never get the chance to do it himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.59,0:17:05.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Smart!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.05,0:17:07.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Twisted!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.95,0:17:14.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Soundwave, do I take your silence to mean you concur with Knock Out's medical expertise?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.58,0:17:22.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Speak now, or forever hold your peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.76,0:17:24.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Going.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.64,0:17:29.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Going...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.33,0:17:43.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Scrap!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.29,0:17:55.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After our deep history together, to not watch the spark end from Optimus's eyes with my very own...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.05,0:18:00.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well-played, scout.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.00,0:18:06.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The chemical formula for the cure you seek.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.83,0:18:09.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not that I expect you to know how to read it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.68,0:18:12.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.09,0:18:19.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And how am I to accomplish terminating Optimus as you proposed,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.19,0:18:22.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,while I'm traped here in a perpetual day-dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.90,0:18:28.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once you release me from this prison, you will have the cure.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.24,0:18:37.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.63,0:18:46.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must guarantee my recovery, or Optimus fades to gunmetal grey.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.42,0:18:48.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The REAL Optimus.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.89,0:18:55.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Arcee, we have the formula.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.99,0:18:57.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Disconnect Bumblebee, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.43,0:19:10.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were watching, you tricked me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.96,0:19:19.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, take me with you! Take me! Take me! Take me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.60,0:19:23.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry, Bee.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.35,0:19:30.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What in...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.38,0:19:34.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Intruders!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.56,0:19:35.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Allow me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.59,0:19:54.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh, it was the inevitable outcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.13,0:20:04.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uhhh... of course it would be wrong to allow Megatron to perish by an Autobot's hand,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.20,0:20:05.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Knock Out.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.80,0:20:22.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it. Steady.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.65,0:20:35.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, reserve the hero's welcome for my physician, and my scout.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.05,0:20:38.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Alright.\N- Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.24,0:20:47.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And how is the patient doing today?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.95,0:20:49.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Funny, you should ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.52,0:20:52.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not sure what the Bots did in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.41,0:20:56.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Megatron's registering zero brainwave activity.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.75,0:20:59.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mmm, meaning?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.12,0:21:03.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Physically he is stable, but now,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.58,0:21:06.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there is no one home.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.81,0:21:19.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm out.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.57,0:21:24.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or should I say, IN!
